case.title: SWF looking for Tall & Professional SWM to date - 33 (Downtown)
case.text: Me: Blonde, cute, curvy and sweet, smart and successful. What I like? 30-42, Big guys, not fat, but like 6 ft+ and 200+ lbs. Clean cut, intelligent, good hearted, educated, well spoken, corporate minded and funny. Looking to actually go on a grown-up date that involves an actual conversation and eye contact. Looking for LTR. Not looking for games, hook-ups, liars or pervs please. Hope to hear from you.
